dcterms:description: MuJoCo environments are used for simulating various robotic tasks, providing a platform for testing reinforcement learning algorithms in continuous control scenarios.

dcterms:description: Ant-v2 is a specific task within the MuJoCo environments aimed at making a four-legged creature walk forward as fast as possible, used to evaluate reinforcement learning algorithms.

dcterms:description: Walker2d-v2 is a task in the MuJoCo environments where the goal is to make a bipedal robot walk forward as quickly as possible, used for testing reinforcement learning methods.
